#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/filetools.rst:108
msgid ""
"Performs a HTTP(S) POST/GET request and returns the HTTP status code and "
"the reply data. If an error occurs then the error code and the message "
"will be returned. Optionally, the result can be written to a file on the "
"disk. By default the algorithm will warn on errors. Optionally, the "
"algorithm can be set to treat HTTP errors as failures."
msgstr ""

